What? Why? What is it?

263
00:16:57,720 --> 00:16:58,800
P'No...

264
00:16:58,800 --> 00:16:59,800
What?

265
00:16:59,800 --> 00:17:01,140
If someone hits on you,

266
00:17:01,140 --> 00:17:02,500
what are you supposed to do?

267
00:17:02,500 --> 00:17:05,000
How am I supposed to know? He's never hit on me!

268
00:17:05,000 --> 00:17:07,320
Before I realized, I already did it with him.

269
00:17:11,653 --> 00:17:14,880
Dude... just now... I saw some guy... He's an International program kid.

270
00:17:14,880 --> 00:17:17,560
He was standing and waiting around the entrance.

271
00:17:17,560 --> 00:17:19,200
Who is it?

272
00:17:19,200 --> 00:17:21,960
I don't know. He's a... International program kid.

273
00:17:21,960 --> 00:17:23,800
He looks arrogant.

274
00:17:23,800 --> 00:17:25,300
He's fair-skinned.

275
00:17:25,300 --> 00:17:27,740
And he doesn't talk to anyone at all.

276
00:17:30,360 --> 00:17:32,000
Hey! Ai'Can!

277
00:17:32,520 --> 00:17:33,940
Where is he off in such a hurry?

278
00:17:33,940 --> 00:17:35,760
- Wait a minute, P'No.
- Huh?

279
00:17:35,760 --> 00:17:38,980
Just now you said... you did it with someone?

280
00:17:39,960 --> 00:17:41,080
Geez...

281
00:17:41,080 --> 00:17:43,320
Well...

282
00:17:43,320 --> 00:17:47,510
I think... It's almost time for practice. I'm going to go change first. I have to practice now. See ya!

283
00:17:47,510 --> 00:17:50,280
Hey, No! Where are you running off to?

284
00:17:51,300 --> 00:17:53,200
So this is what he's like now?

285
00:17:53,200 --> 00:17:55,360
That was quick as hell.

286
00:17:55,360 --> 00:17:56,920
Let's go. Let's go. Let's practice.

287
00:17:56,920 --> 00:17:58,920
Come on, Bro.

288
00:18:06,100 --> 00:18:07,960
Why did you come here?

289
00:18:08,680 --> 00:18:10,760
I'm here to score some points.

290
00:18:10,760 --> 00:18:12,640
What points? Playing football?

291
00:18:12,640 --> 00:18:14,380
But you don't play football.

292
00:18:14,380 --> 00:18:17,360
Oh! You're here to score points with my captain.

293
00:18:17,360 --> 00:18:18,840
Our team is full already.

294
00:18:18,840 --> 00:18:20,880
We're not accepting any more members.

295
00:18:21,580 --> 00:18:23,900
You know what I mean.

296
00:18:24,880 --> 00:18:26,760
I don't know at all...

297
00:18:26,760 --> 00:18:30,080
I'm so stupid. I don't understand anything...

298
00:18:34,900 --> 00:18:36,820
Your face is red.

299
00:18:38,380 --> 00:18:39,640
Whose face is red?

300
00:18:39,640 --> 00:18:42,180
I'm not being shy, you know.

301
00:18:42,840 --> 00:18:44,700
If you're not shy, then you're not shy.

302
00:18:45,960 --> 00:18:47,760
I bought this for you.

303
00:18:49,840 --> 00:18:52,680
I know that you can't be bought with money,

304
00:18:52,680 --> 00:18:54,160
but it's just snacks.

305
00:18:54,160 --> 00:18:56,200
You could probably accept it, right?

306
00:18:58,900 --> 00:19:02,340
If it's just snacks… then...

307
00:19:02,900 --> 00:19:04,360
They all look so freaking yummy!

308
00:19:04,360 --> 00:19:06,040
Look at this.

309
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:09,620
Lucky me, Ai'Can.

310
00:19:09,620 --> 00:19:11,185
Can.

311
00:19:27,420 --> 00:19:29,480
Payment for the snacks.

312
00:19:29,480 --> 00:19:32,700
I told you already. I'm here to score points.

313
00:19:48,000 --> 00:19:51,160
Why do I have to get kissed by him again??

314
00:19:51,160 --> 00:19:54,600
And why does my heart have to beat so fast like this, too?

315
00:19:58,000 --> 00:20:00,000
This looks so freaking yummy!

316
00:20:00,180 --> 00:20:01,740
Look at this!

317
00:20:01,740 --> 00:20:03,300
Which one should I eat first?

318
00:20:03,300 --> 00:20:05,580
It's full of so many things!

319
00:20:19,600 --> 00:20:22,080
I chose everything by myself you know.

320
00:20:22,080 --> 00:20:24,700
I hope that you will like it, P'No.

321
00:20:50,640 --> 00:20:54,380
If you like something really hot and spicy, then eat the Bento.

322
00:21:05,900 --> 00:21:10,720
But if you like it mild, then drink Jele Vita Bead.

323
00:21:19,380 --> 00:21:20,940
I miss you.

324
00:21:20,940 --> 00:21:23,300
I know that you don't want to see me yet,

325
00:21:23,300 --> 00:21:25,400
but I do miss you.

326
00:21:26,800 --> 00:21:29,480
Geez! That crazy kid!

327
00:21:48,040 --> 00:21:53,600
[Thanks for the phone, man. I'll definitely pay you back.]

328
00:21:59,740 --> 00:22:03,120
Hello, man. Why are you calling?

329
00:22:03,120 --> 00:22:04,800
Calling makes it easier to talk.

330
00:22:04,800 --> 00:22:06,600
Texting to talk is pretty easy too though.

331
00:22:06,600 --> 00:22:08,760
I almost finished typing.

332
00:22:10,520 --> 00:22:12,440
Do you like your new phone?

333
00:22:12,440 --> 00:22:14,840
I like it so much, man! It's even faster than my old one.

334
00:22:14,840 --> 00:22:16,380
It's so smooth when playing games!

335
00:22:16,460 --> 00:22:18,480
I don't know if it's good luck or bad luck

336
00:22:18,480 --> 00:22:21,640
